data.description: This is and excellent opportunity to own this beautiful 2 SFR on a lot property located in Fontana. unit A comprise of 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms ,living room and eating area of living room, kitchen , inside laundry room, with separate electrical and gas meters. total living space 1564 sq ft. Unit B is 1 bedroom, 1 Bathroom, living room, kitchen with Island and granite counter tops, eating are of the kitchen, cover patio. landscaped rear yard, total living space 899 sq ft, long cemented drive way, theirs a block wall wrought Iron fence , wrought iron gate , fruit trees. close to transportation, shopping centers, Victoria Garden, Ontario Mills , Parks and Schools. close access to 10 and 60 freeways.
